column5: i was thinking of taking a camping trip and was wondering if there any good bass lakes up there
Joeis a very good Bass Lake

TONS of great bass lakes. Some BIG smallies to be had!  The park is MASSIVE, so you'd need to tell us what area you wanted to go to.  Do yourself a favour and download this map of the park. It shows all the portages, distances, etc.
it really doesn;t matter where i go  iam open to any where i got all week
